# PHP OOP â€“ Caneta Exercise

This repository contains a simple Object-Oriented Programming exercise in PHP.

## Concepts covered
- Classes and objects
- Encapsulation
- Private attributes
- Getters and setters
- Basic validation
- Object state control

## Description
The `Caneta` class models a pen with attributes such as model, color, tip size, and capped state.  
All attributes are private and accessed only through methods, ensuring data integrity.
